:1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T05:53:33.000Z","msg":"49000們FF也就有了空間。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T06:18:46.000Z","msg":"一句就穿晒煲擺明引戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c14d14b8fdefde6e262a7ff8cfb05fe850990de9","tid":987054,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T14:17:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"455c5708880b74ddd39e35fc21c8a873d7f0c51a","tid":987054,"uid":34981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T14:37:20.000Z","msg":"咖喱牛腩：利物浦小心曼聯呀"},{"pid":"175389ef6908d4a936f0e94173c5181499cce015","tid":987054,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T14:37:58.000Z","msg":"獌狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9e02b5df56455db6bfd786dcc735b022df97c0a","tid":987054,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T14:38:31.000Z","msg":"呢個作者直頭係仆街到全能，六隊抽哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49f572baa4eb77a49aa73a08a37fc578a2280125","tid":987054,"uid":52571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T14:39:35.000Z","msg":"會員曼聯名宿黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"600e6cba90972410be3743bf6d5c06cbff21f247","tid":987054,"uid":33730,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T14:40:48.000Z","msg":"樓主寫完自己po返上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04d4a9b6d86f42a8f4cc7fc61831918632527189","tid":987054,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"